{
  "texts": [
    "Second, one needs to ensure that the model robustly pursues those goals.",
    "12 The first challenge has been termed the 'king Midas problem' (Russell 2019).",
    "In a nutshell, human goals are complex, multi-faceted, diverse, wide-ranging, and potentially inconsistent.",
    "This is why it is exceedingly hard, if not impossible, to explicitly specify everything humans tend to care about.",
    "An explicit list is bound to forget some important goals which will then be neglected by AI."
  ]
}